# Project Information

- **Project Name**: OneJs DDD Boilerplate
- **Framework**: OneJs (`.oneJs/`) — custom DDD framework with DI, EntityBase, ValueObjectBase, EventBus, Logger, plugin system
- **Description**: Monorepo boilerplate following DDD principles with Hexagonal Architecture (Ports & Adapters)

## Framework Imports

```typescript
import { Entity, EntityBase, ValueObject, ValueObjectBase } from '@OneJs/core'
import { Injectable, Inject, Logger, OneJsError, ErrorCodes } from '@OneJs/core'
import { EventBus } from '@OneJs/event-bus'
```

